    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such stunning condition that it still has that 'new car' feel\u2014I've babied it since day one! Everything is spotless, and it drives like a dream. I know my seller score is just getting started, but I promise you won\u2019t find a cleaner ride for this price. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
