    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine example of the E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders and benefits from a recent valve adjustment. The double VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components for optimal variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound with reinforced subframe mounting points and fresh polyurethane bushings throughout. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of orange peel or oxidation, while the interior features flawless Nappa leather and functional electronics. This is a collector-grade specimen optimized for the purist.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
