    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, entirely free from stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Every body panel is original and perfectly aligned. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, the dashboard remains flawless, and the interior still carries a faint factory scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive, folder-bound service history with every maintenance milestone performed ahead of schedule by certified specialists. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. This is a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover.",
