    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect valve clearances and a recently overhauled dual-VANOS system using upgraded seals and rattle kits. The 'Big Three' have been addressed: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates, and the rod bearings were replaced with treated shells and ARP hardware. Power is transmitted through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to a factory-spec variable M-differential. The chassis remains taut, featuring refreshed bushings and original dampers that retain their factory-specified rebound characteristics. The exterior paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing no signs of orange peel or previous collision repair. A purist\u2019s example with zero mechanical compromises.",
